- requesty pro subscribe/unsubcsribe eventu pro connection
  - prip. naplanovat odeslani vseho pri pripojeni

- blokovat odesilani zmeny konfigurace ve stejnem kanalu

- adv list - timeout

- io_port state btjp command
- factory reset btjp command

- zvazit ruzne skupiny pro logovani (pripadne CONFIG_LOG_FUNC_NAME_PREFIX_xxxx)

- oboje settings.c -- zvazit zda nepresunout do extra modulu a nespoustet eventem

- zvazit odstraneni nastaveni potu/pinu - mozna bude stacit jen nastaveni celeho profilu

----

| state |  button | action | signalling |
|-------|---------|--------|------------|
| connected, connecting | long press 2 | disconnect & start scanning | no signalling |
| scanning | long press 2 | delete bond #1, start pairing #1 | blink |
| connected | hold 1 + press 2 (x1, x2, x3) | select profile | blink
| any | long press 1 | start SPI | blink







